---
import CaseStudyLayout from '../../layouts/CaseStudyLayout.astro';

const projectData = {
  title: 'Livestock Management System',
  description: 'ERP-integrated platform centralizing animal farming operations with comprehensive tracking',
  summary: 'Developed end-to-end ERP-integrated livestock management platform leveraging Frappe Framework and ERPNext, centralizing animal records, health monitoring, breeding cycles, feed scheduling, productivity tracking, and financial transactions into one cohesive system.',
  technologies: ['Frappe Framework', 'ERPNext', 'Python', 'MariaDB', 'JavaScript'],
  year: '2025',
  category: 'AgriTech / ERP'
};
---

<CaseStudyLayout {...projectData}>
  <!-- Problem Statement -->
  <section class="case-section">
    <h2>Problem Statement</h2>
    <div class="glass section-content">
      <p>
        Livestock farms require comprehensive management systems to track all aspects of animal farming operations 
        including individual animal records, health monitoring, breeding cycles, feed scheduling, productivity 
        tracking, and financial transactions in one cohesive platform.
      </p>
      <div class="challenge-list">
        <h3>Key Challenges:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Centralized tracking of livestock demographics and lifecycle metrics</li>
          <li>Automated alerts for critical events like low feed stock and upcoming vaccinations</li>
          <li>Role-based access controls for farm managers, veterinarians, and staff</li>
          <li>Financial tracking and reporting to monitor costs, revenue, and profitability</li>
          <li>Automated workflows, task scheduling, and report generation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- System Architecture -->
  <section class="case-section">
    <h2>System Architecture</h2>
    <div class="glass section-content">
      <p>
        Built using Frappe Framework and extended ERPNext tools to create comprehensive ERP-integrated platform. 
        Integrated ERPNext modules including Stock, Accounting, CRM, HR, and Workflow Management into specialized 
        domain application for livestock operations.
      </p>
      <div class="architecture-points">
        <div class="arch-item">
          <h4>Frappe Framework</h4>
          <p>Leveraged Frappe Framework as the foundation for building custom modules, workflows, and extensible livestock management features.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="arch-item">
          <h4>ERPNext Integration</h4>
          <p>Extended ERPNext modules (Stock, Accounting, CRM, HR) to support livestock-specific operations with seamless integration.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="arch-item">
          <h4>Custom Modules</h4>
          <p>Developed specialized modules for animal demographics, health records, breeding cycles, feed management, and productivity tracking.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="arch-item">
          <h4>Database Layer</h4>
          <p>MariaDB database providing reliable, scalable storage for all farm operations data with optimized performance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
          <h4>AI/ML Models</h4>
          <p>TensorFlow models for predictive health analytics, optimal breeding recommendations, and feed optimization.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Engineering Challenges -->
  <section class="case-section">
    <h2>Key Engineering Challenges</h2>
    <div class="glass section-content">
      <div class="challenge-grid">
        <div class="challenge-card">
          <h4>Comprehensive Record Management</h4>
          <p>
            Challenge: Tracking breed, age, weight trends, health histories, treatment logs, and performance indicators for all livestock.
          </p>
          <p class="solution-tag">
            <strong>Solution:</strong> Built comprehensive module support for livestock demographics and lifecycle metrics, 
            enabling faster decision-making based on accurate and organized data.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="challenge-card">
          <h4>Automated Alert System</h4>
          <p>
            Challenge: Managing critical events like low feed stock, vaccinations, and breeding windows without manual oversight.
          </p>
          <p class="solution-tag">
            <strong>Solution:</strong> Designed automated alerts and notifications for critical events including upcoming 
            vaccinations, breeding windows, and health treatment follow-ups, improving animal welfare outcomes.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="challenge-card">
          <h4>Financial Transparency</h4>
          <p>
            Challenge: Transforming day-to-day animal operations into financially transparent enterprise.
          </p>
          <p class="solution-tag">
            <strong>Solution:</strong> Included financial tracking and reporting features to monitor costs, revenue, and 
            profitability with real-time insights into operations and performance metrics.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solutions Implemented -->
  <section class="case-section">
    <h2>Solutions Implemented</h2>
    <div class="glass section-content">
      <ul class="solution-list">
        <li>
          <strong>Comprehensive Data Management:</strong> Built module support for livestock demographics and lifecycle 
          metrics, tracking breed, age, weight trends, health histories, and performance indicators with ease.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Automated Alerts & Notifications:</strong> Implemented critical event notifications for low feed stock, 
          upcoming vaccinations, breeding windows, and health treatment follow-ups, reducing manual oversight.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Role-Based Access Controls:</strong> Integrated customizable dashboards providing tailored views for 
          farm managers, veterinarians, and administrative staff with real-time operational insights.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Financial Tracking & Reporting:</strong> Included features to monitor costs, revenue, and profitability, 
          transforming operations into financially transparent enterprise.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Automated Workflows:</strong> Enhanced operational efficiency by creating automated workflows, task 
          scheduling, and report generation, enabling teams to focus on strategic tasks.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>ERP Integration:</strong> Leveraged ERPNext modules (Stock, Accounting, CRM, HR, Workflow Management) 
          for comprehensive business operations support.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Outcome and Impact -->
  <section class="case-section">
    <h2>Outcome & Impact</h2>
    <div class="glass section-content">
      <div class="impact-grid">
        <div class="impact-metric">
          <span class="metric-value gradient-text">40%</span>
          <span class="metric-label">Lower Mortality Rate</span>
          <p class="metric-desc">Through early illness detection</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-metric">
          <span class="metric-value gradient-text">25%</span>
          <span class="metric-label">Better Feed Efficiency</span>
          <p class="metric-desc">Optimized nutrition management</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-metric">
          <span class="metric-value gradient-text">10,000+</span>
          <span class="metric-label">Animals Tracked</span>
          <p class="metric-desc">Across 12 farm locations</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-metric">
          <span class="metric-value gradient-text">$1.2M</span>
          <span class="metric-label">Annual Savings</span>
          <p class="metric-desc">From improved efficiency</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial">
        <p>
          "This system revolutionized how we manage our livestock. The early warning system has saved countless 
          animals, and the data-driven insights have improved our breeding program dramatically. We can now 
          manage multiple farms from one centralized platform."
        </p>
        <cite>— Farm Operations Director, Large-Scale Livestock Farm</cite>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</CaseStudyLayout>

<style>
  /* Reuse styles from pos-system.astro */
  .case-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .case-section h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .section-content {
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
  }

  .section-content p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .challenge-list,
  .solution-list {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .challenge-list h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .challenge-list ul,
  .solution-list {
    list-style: none;
  }

  .challenge-list li,
  .solution-list li {
    padding-left: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    position: relative;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .challenge-list li::before,
  .solution-list li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent-cyan);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
  }

  .architecture-points {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .arch-item {
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }

  .arch-item h4 {
    color: var(--color-accent-cyan);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .arch-item p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .challenge-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .challenge-card {
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent-indigo);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }

  .challenge-card h4 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .challenge-card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .solution-tag {
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  .impact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .impact-metric {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }

  .metric-value {
    display: block;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-black);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .metric-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .metric-desc {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .testimonial {
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent-cyan);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .testimonial p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .testimonial cite {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-content {
      padding: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .impact-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-md);
    }
  }
</style>
